      <h1>Poetry</h1>
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Fleeting</h2>
        <p>
          Moments, like rivers, rush and fade,<br>
          Leaving whispers where memories played.<br>
          A breath, a thought, a step, a sighâ€”<br>
          All vanish beneath the endless sky.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Abstract Horizon</h2>
        <p>
          What is truth if not a shape,<br>
          That shifts with light and thought's escape?<br>
          Words may frame what can't be caught,<br>
          And silence echo all we've sought.
        </p>
      </div>

